{"tid":2011832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母親節晚咁癲嘅原因","createTime":"2020-05-11T09:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T14:04:49.000Z","uid":166032,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6241949aa181ad3150ff22eeaab5f72bee81aa3","tid":2011832,"uid":166032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"1. 25KG一定係用黎賣，否則你一野啪晒佢我當無數<br />\n<br />\n2. 咩人會同個艇買毒品？老同去警署買？雖然唔可以話無可能，但最大嫌疑係佢身邊嘅人；例如黑警除左黑警外都無朋友，咁佢俾返同事嘅機會都好大；成人吸毒有唔少案例係由同事間分享開始<br />\n<br />\n3. 不過販毒不嬲查上唔查下，會查毒品來源，但好少查賣俾邊個<br />\n<br />\n4. 但接貨嘅身有屎嘅應該驚列瀨即刻掉晒，唔通擺低等拉？<br />\n<br />\n5. 咁掉晒斷癮會點呢？會出現一系列戒斷症狀，包括脾氣暴躁，失眠，顫抖，焦慮，屙嘔等等；部份會有精神病症狀，幻覺幻聽，妄想被迫害等<br />\n<br />\nMATCH!"},{"pid":"04c05ded805e7736ed9b6a811958f8681278add3","tid":2011832,"uid":320192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"雪糕筒 Airbnb 自導自演 僭建 冰毒 曲解法律"},{"pid":"902a3c7bae07a9ac7d4ce7ad9581cc8751a6a689","tid":2011832,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:13:47.000Z","msg":"支持黑警食刨冰，隊到手軟腳軟，好似清末咁毒品氾濫就係港共末日"},{"pid":"35524a7e0317d6900d837be55c824af40673cd89","tid":2011832,"uid":2645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差 當差有冰hi"},{"pid":"0d59ee1e6ea9ba9ad6c29e85bfc70c6bb6cd57ad","tid":2011832,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"支持警察隊冰舒緩壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc8cba3f86a87726328b1cc2dcad7fa0e0cbaba","tid":2011832,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ef548336071996f3e2bb1dc2a6f1d0735c83fa","tid":2011832,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T10:56:10.000Z","msg":"台灣啊！"},{"pid":"3627f84c29f5fbdea8e62b224